+ * skeleton MURAM-resident allocation pair:
+ *
+ *   - the per-manip HMTD (Header Manipulation Table Descriptor),
+ *     16 bytes, MURAM-resident, opCode=0x00 (no manip) until body-2;
+ *   - the per-manip HMCT (Header Manipulation Command Table), 64 byte
+ *     scratch region for the variant-specific command sequence written
