+ * mutation (add/remove of struct fman_pcd_manip on pcd->manip_list)
+ * and the per-manip MURAM budget update at manip granularity.
+ * Per-manip manip->lock is a spinlock; reserved for body-2 (variant
+ * encoders may run from softirq context on flow-table updates that
+ * recreate a manip to apply a runtime NAT change).  The CC walker
